title: Kristen Bell / Depression, Anxiety and a side of Eczema
description: Dr. Wali debunks Sean's fear of dying from drinking too much water. We also have the charming Kristen Bell on to bring light Anxiety, Depression and a dash on Eczema. K-Bell takes on Sean in a heated battle of "Dr. Wali's Hall of Fame."
